g.text: 1. Q is undefined until R is asserted2. Q → ‘1’ when S is asserted3. Q → '0' when R is asserted4. Q → '1' when S is asserted5. Q stays at '1' when S & R asserted6. Q → '0' when R asserted, S de-asserted
